						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/07/my-rnn-interview-snowden-disclosures-cause-outrage-across-eu.html" title="18:42" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-07-12T18:42:19+00:00" pubdate>July 12, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/07/my-rnn-interview-snowden-disclosures-cause-outrage-across-eu.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here is a recent inter­view I did for the <a href="http://therealnews.com/t2/">Real News Net­work</a> about the global and European fall-out from the Edward Snowden dis­clos­ures:<br />
